data.title: EvoEMD: Cosmic Evolution with an Early Matter-Dominated era
data.name: EvoEMD
data.description: Evolution with an Early Matter-Dominated era

evidence: Owner metadata shows GitHub user account: owner_type=User, owner_login=ycwu1030, with no mention of an institution or group in README, indicating an individual maintainer.

README describes EvoEMD as “A framework to evaluate the evolution w/ or w/o an early matter dominated (EMD) era” and provides example executables in `EvoEMD/build/bin`, indicating it is run as an application for cosmology calculations.

README states it “Solv[es] the Boltzmann equation using 4th order Runge-Kutta… tailored to Cosmology application” and references a paper to cite when using EvoEMD, showing it directly produces research-relevant cosmological results.
